<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171100>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pseudione minimocrenulata: A, 12 mm female, dorsal view; B, 12 mm female, ventral view; C, male, dorsal view; D, male, ventral view. Scale bars: A, B = 5 mm; C, D = 1.75 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171100/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171102>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Pseudione minimocrenulata, 11.5 mm female: A, oostegite I, internal view; B, maxilliped, outer view; C, maxilliped, inner view; D, left side of barbula. Scale bar = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171102/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171101>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Pseudione minimocrenulata, 11.5 mm female: A, antennule; B, tip of antennule; C, antenna; D, antennal tip; E, pereopod I; F, pereopod VII (right detail showing unidentified protist tests). Scale bars: B, D = 0.125 mm; A, C, E, F = 0.75 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171101/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171103>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Pseudione minimocrenulata, male: A, antennule (distal); B, antennular tip; C, antenna (distal); D, antennal tip; E, pereopod I; F, pereopod VII. Scale bars: B, D = 0.2 mm; A, C, E, F = 0.75 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171103/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

